npm i -D nodemon concurrently

express-validators

heroku deployment
- 调整项目结构: 将client folder放在server下面
- 在server.js中添加serve static folder (/client/build/index.html)
- 在server的package.json中定义heroku-postbuild
- heroku login
- git init
- git add .
- heroku git:remote -a mighty-fjord-85520
- git push heroku master


